Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with someone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:15.79,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"From Now On"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, I'm in love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've heard that when you're in love,\Nthe world starts to look totally different...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my case, I haven't noticed\Nany significant changes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, uglyface!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, that's the first thing\Nthat comes out of your mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kindly cover that mouth of\Nyours, will you? It's unseemly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... When I see\Nthose winter uniforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it reminds me of when you kneed me\Nthat first day we met,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it gives me the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of getting kneed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is this what you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think\Nyou're doing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your new girlfriend just\Nshowed up in her new uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about a little praise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're cute. Yes, you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not good, not good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I jumping for joy\Nover such blatant lip service?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, well, I guess I might have\Nchanged in some small ways.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like feeling so elated over\Nthe most trivial things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Ichijo and Chitoge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raku Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard... how could you,\Nwhen you have Young Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like getting even more\Npissed at annoying things!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever the case,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as you can see, the romance\NI'd always yearned for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is something I'm being forced\Nto share with this guy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now then, how is this\Ngoing to turn out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait! Seriously, how is\Nthis going to turn out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hold up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's good that I know\NI'm in love with this guy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:49.11,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raku and Chitoge's\NNEXT STAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but what happens next?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I like him, then does that mean, uh...\Nthat I want to date him or something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, not be his fake\Ngirlfriend, but his real girlfriend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mmm, that doesn't feel right somehow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the first place, what would\Nwe do if we were dating?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like... walk home\Ntogether after school...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}stop for snacks on the way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}go on dates on our days off...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! Isn't that the same thing\Nwe're doing now anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then does this mean that I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...want this guy to like me, maybe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come hither! Come hither!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me in that creepy way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a feeling that's close.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow that just doesn't feel right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait! What am I gonna do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I'm getting seriously confused!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of relationship\Ndo I want with him, exactly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got your locket back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Well, for what it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I should\Nlet you three know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! This makes me\Nfeel so complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:05:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That you got it back safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without further ado! Let's open up\Nthat locket with this key, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold up a second, Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where's the harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now you'll finally know\Nwho your first love was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, although it had to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At last, we'll have proof that it was I\Nwho promised you my hand in marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come, come! You two\Nstanding there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're dying to find out\Nas well. I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jump the gun like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That we need to open it\Njust yet, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chitoge?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, because! See...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to rush into it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It might be better to wait\Ntill things settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, this is just something\Nthat happened when we were kids, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just the other day, she was\Nall fired up to get to the bottom of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, Kirisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must really be terrified to find out\Nthat you weren't his soulmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!\NThat's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I kind of want to know, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If... No matter who opens it, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was something that\Nhappened when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I do want to,\Nyou know, find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm telling you,\Nhold up, hold up, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's still broken, all right? This locket.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so long story short...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got as far as extracting\Nthe stuck key and fixing it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something stuck\Nin the back of the locket,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and there's no way to open\Nthe lock by normal means.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could get it out\Nby smashing it open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your call?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Shu,\Nabout that photo book...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, but if it's not fixed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An autographed limited edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't break it! Don't break it!\NThis is important to me, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually we might\Nfind a way to open it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I want you to wait till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if we still can't figure it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you think you just\Nhave to know the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then let's bust this open\Nand take a look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, maybe that'll give us a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not having to break it\Nwould be best, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I wonder what it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An object that can be placed\Nin something this size.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said we would take it out together\Nwhen we were reunited, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An engagement ring, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're all very funny.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I got all nervous for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do\Nto make up for this letdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I tried to tell you\Nguys right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... If we'd gotten the locket open,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what in the world would've happened?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If my key had opened it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If... my key hadn't opened it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I just went on\Nhaving feelings for him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and then found out later\Nthat I wasn't his soul mate,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}how would I feel, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was something\Nthat happened when we were kids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't stop thinking about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, what am I gonna do?\NI'm starting to feel uneasy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I still don't even know\Nhow I want this to turn out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do I want it to turn out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do I want things to stay\Nthe way they are now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, but unless I make a move,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he'll never realize\Nhow I feel about him, will he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chitoge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, don't you think you're\Nacting kind of weird today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw your face,\NI thought, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But are you...\Njust like I thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me... He noticed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How I feel about him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... Did my face\Nreally give me away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no, no...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not this moron of all people,\Nno way would he...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course he's going to\Nsay something lame.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't you say\Nsomething sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hungry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I spend so much time with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I pretty much know\Nwhat makes you tick now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have this intense look\Non your face over something,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but when you have that look,\Nit's usually when you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you didn't\Nhave much for lunch, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're on a diet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, well!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll think about\Nthe complicated stuff later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, treat me to ramen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so you are hungry after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.79,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Please Notice"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My lips are so dry these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitogecchi, don't you wear lip gloss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lip gloss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second! I'll lend you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bought this lip gloss the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the kind that\Nmakes your lips all supple!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you look totally adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really look good\Nwith it on, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look so good, you're\Nmaking me jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Curse you\Nand your model's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You rock anything\Nyou wear, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you like it, you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. To be honest, I didn't\Nknow what to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, you look\Nbetter in it, Chitogecchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna make Ichijo\Ngo all weak at the knees, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and put it on\Nagain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-Is that right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will he think I look cute?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He couldn't be more dense, so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, morning, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's even chillier\Nthan usual today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did we have\Nfor first period again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,English, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there was\Nany homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, he missed it\Nspectacularly, didn't he now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although I did expect as much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come to think of it,\Nyou know winter's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is the season for\Nfeeling dry, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh... I was thinking\Nhow dry my lips get.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lips?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My lips always get chapped in winter,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm like, "Ouch!"\Nand there's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it takes forever\Nto heal, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? Notice them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, I practically\Nshoved them in your face!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why, you...! What are you gonna do\Nabout this tiny courage I've mustered...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on! Are you trying to tell me\NI'm not even a speck in your eye?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit! I'm not gonna let it\Nend like this, you know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're wearing\Nlip gloss today, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that it's come to this, I'm gonna\Nmake him notice or die trying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But lip gloss alone isn't gonna\Ncut it for that oblivious fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, bean sprout!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, morn—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, somehow today is, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to yesterday, it's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The air feels a little warmer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well? The shampoo I used this morning is\N5,000 yen more expensive than my usual one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must've noticed\Nthat, at least, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you sniff this sweet fragrance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking it's\Ncolder than yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-Y-You miserable jerk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}D-Did you just dismiss my secret\Nweapon shampoo with one sneeze?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why, you dumbass!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're nothing but a bean sprout!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing but a bean sprout!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's calm down a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even girls don't always\Nnotice lip gloss or shampoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder that moron didn't\Nnotice it either - it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to be more\Nblatant with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I almost never do my nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think they look pretty cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something this obvious,\Nhe's sure to notice, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the handout\NI borrowed the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it back to you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now then... Comments, please?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Huh? Hey... ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you\Nthink you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Comments, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I'll pound\Nyou with my fist next?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you get like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jeez!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never dreamed he was\Nthis much of an idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You dummy! Dummy!\NDummy! Dummy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why don't you notice them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or is it that you do notice,\Nbut you have no comment?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either way, it's so frustrating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that it's come to this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that it's come to this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This should do it! This should\Ndo it! What do you say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's sure to notice this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and if it's this drastic a change,\Nhe won't be able to ignore it, will he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that ribbon part of a makeover?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-My, my, darling, you're late today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey... morning, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of overslept today, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All that homework\Nyesterday, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to get it all done\Nas soon as I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it was harder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that we have to\Nturn it in any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on! Wh-Why\Nare you ignoring me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me you don't\Neven notice this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that even possible?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything you'd\Nlike to say about me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of answer is that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too, now that you mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My shoulders got all stiff\Nfrom studying yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You hitting the books, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you weren't watching\Nsome TV show and lazing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why won't he say anything?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me he really\Nhasn't noticed it yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if he has noticed, I'm sure\Nthere'd be some kind of reaction!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just how dense is he, anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jeez! I don't believe this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This ribbon was my\Nmost alluring feature!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I get him to notice it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or is it that he couldn't\Ncare less about me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Your lunch today,\Nit's not the usual Kobe beef,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but Iberico ham, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vitamins are good for\Nyou, right? Yep, vitamins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what you notice?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For God's sake, cow or pig? I only\Njust found that out myself now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does this mean the change\Nin me is less important?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soooo annoying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, man, I'm so frustrated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Notice it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Notice it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Notice it!!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Mr. Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to test your\Nabilities as a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please point out any changes\Nyou've noticed in me recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This feels so futile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you changed somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, I mean, you've\Ntotally changed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to me\Nlike you've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Have you gained a little weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-M-M-My bad!\NI was just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Did you cut your bangs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you wearing mascara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are natural, I'll have you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you grow taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who grows that fast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your new diet...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to clock you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know about\Nany other changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriously, why did I have to go\Nand fall for a guy like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't about you wearing lip\Ngloss for the last three days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you noticed that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that the change\Nyou're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then... what about the shampoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you did change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And my nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I guess I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say anything\Nwhen you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to\Nsay stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, even if I did notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,guys normally don't go around\Nsaying, "Hey, looking good," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold up, forget I just said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, forget it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it would be weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I say\Nstuff like that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For a girl, whether or not you notice\Nthat kind of thing is so crucial!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be popular with girls,\Nwhy don't you put some thought into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because you didn't\Nthink I looked good?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that I didn't look cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go that far, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose you were\Nrather cute, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what do you\Nthink of this ribbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your usual one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean\Nyou never noticed it?
